quote: Main udna chahta hun Naina. Daudna chahta hun, Girna bhi chahta hun. Bas, rukna nahi chahta.
author: Bunny

quote: Life mein jitna bhi try karo, kuch na kuch toh chootega hi. Isiye yahin, isi pal ka mazza lete hain.
author: Naina

quote: Tum pehle bhi itni khoobsurat thi ya waqt ne kiya koi haseen sitam?
author: Bunny

quote: Pata nahi.Kuch logon ke saath rehne se hi sab theek ho jata hai.
author: Aditi

quote: Shaadi is daal chawal for pachaas saal till you die. Arey life mein thoda bahut kheema pav, tangdi kebab, hakka noodles bhi hona chahiye na!
author: Bunny

quote: Tu right nahi hai Naina, bas mujhse bahut alag hai.
author: Bunny

quote: Yaadein mithai ke dabbe ki tarah hoti hain, ek baar khula toh sirf ek tukda nahi khaa paoge.
author: Naina

quote: Khud pe daya karna band karo, aur khud se pyaar karna seekho.
author: Bunny

quote: 22 tak padhai, 25 pe naukri, 26 pe chokri, 30 pe bachche, 60 pe retirement , aur phir maut ka intezaar.Dhat! aisi ghisi piti life thodi jeena chahta hoon!
author: Bunny

quote: Guzarta wakt hain lekin kharch hum hote hain
author: Bunny

quote: Kahi pe pahuchne ke liye kahin se nikalna bahut zaruri hota hain. Sahi wakt pe kat lena chahiye nahi toh gile-shiqwe hone lagte hain
author: Bunny

quote: Abey dhongi! Cheating nahi karta toh ab tak 2nd standard mein hota
author: Naina

quote: Haath ka mail hota hain paisa.Isse bacha te nahi, udaate hain
author: Bunny

quote: Ek baad yaad rakhna. Zindagi mein chahe kuch bhi ho jaye, kuch bhi. Main humesha tumhare saath hoon
author: Bunny's dad

quote: Saale apne dollar se khareed raha hain mujhe? Itni sasti nahi hain meri dosti
author: Avi

quote: Maine kaha tha na. Kuch waqt do. Sab theek ho jaayega
author: Naina

quote: Yeh pahad chadna tumhare liye sirf trekking hoga. Mere liye nasha hain
author: Bunny
